'There is no substitute for class and Daniel has it on and off the field, as a player and as a person.'

The 29-year-old central defender moved to the Danish side for £3million after eight years at Anfield.

Agger has made 232 appearances for the Merseyside club, but has only lifted a single trophy - the 2012 Carling Cup at Wembley.

